high_descs: Turn around, walk towards the window and turn left towards the small table
Pick up the candle from the table.
Turn around and walk towards the tall standing lamp.
Raise the candle up to the lamp shade to turn on the lamp.
anns.task_desc: Turn on the standing lamp with the candle.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the small table in the right back corner of the room.
Pick up the green candle on the table.
Turn left and walk to the other corner of the room with the lamp in it.
Turn on the lamp.
anns.task_desc: Look at a candle with the illumination of a lamp.

high_descs: Move to the round white table in the far corner of the room
Pick up the green candle on top of the table
Carry the candle to the large floor lamp in the opposite corner of the room
Turn on the lamp
anns.task_desc: Carry a green candle while turning on a lamp

high_descs: Turn right and walk to the couch then turn right and walk past the couch on your left and when you do turn left and walk to the wall then turn right and take a step backwards.
Pick up the candle that's in front of you.
Turn around and walk to the light that's in front of you.
Turn on the light.
anns.task_desc: Inspect a candle by lamp light.

high_descs: Turn to your right and walk across the room, between the couch and the windows, to the small round end table in the far right corner.
Pick up the green candle near the edge of the small, round table.
Turn around and walk between the TV and the coffee table, to the lamp in the right corner of the room.
Turn that lamp on while holding the green candle.
anns.task_desc: Turn the lamp on while holding a candle.

high_descs: Turn around and move behind the sofa until you get to the small table in the corner and move to the left side of it.
Pick  the white candle up from the table, which will be the object closest to you.
Turn and cross the room, moving between the coffee table and entertainment console until you get to a tall shelf in the corner.
Place the candle on the shelf and light it.
anns.task_desc: Move a candle to a shelf and light it.
